Impossible Engineering: Series 3
Behind every seemingly impossible marvel of modern engineering is a cast of historic trailblazers who designed new building techniques, took risks on untested materials and revolutionised their field. Brand new series, 'Impossible Engineering', is a tribute to their achievements.

3)  Worlds Tallest 
The engineering behind the tallest things in the world. The Shard is the tallest building in Western Europe at 309.6 meters. It has enough glass panels to cover 130 basketball courts!
